      "546:text": "transform the image to realistic photograph，动漫转BJD娃娃，动漫转写实真人,和原图一样的表情控制，电影级光影",
      "554:weight_dtype": "default",
      "562:text_0": "```text\n[SUBJECT], a stunningly beautiful, hyper-realistic young woman with lavender-purple hair styled in a high ponytail, wearing a red and white Christmas-style bodysuit with fur trim and a jingle bell necklace, and sheer white thigh-high stockings, sitting on a white bed sheet, posing with a finger pressed to her lips in a \"shushing\" gesture, looking directly into the camera with a playful, alluring, and slightly mischievous expression, soft pink eyes, large and detailed with moisture and distinct catchlights, soft anime-style illustration, soft studio lighting, bright and airy atmosphere, clean white background, subsurface scattering on skin, smooth skin texture, high-resolution, masterpiece, 8k, best quality, sharp focus, visual fidelity of a high-end 3D render, octane render, ray tracing\n```",
